snippet.title: Sinbad's Journey  - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Sinbad's Journey walkthrough by Carmel Games:
The famous sailor Sinbad is ready for another big journey throughout the seas, but first he must make an unplanned stop to fix his ship.
Play at http://snapbreak.com/puzzle/sinbads-journey
